Sentencas: LSM(La(Sr)MnO3)/YSZ(Y2O3 stabilized ZrO2) composite cathode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFCs) was fabricated by using the composite particle consisting of well-dispersed nano-size grains of LSM and YSZ.
Titulo: Morphology control of the electrode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells by using nanoparticles

Sentencas: The composite cathode had a porous structure as well as uniformly dispersed fine LSM and YSZ grains.
Titulo: Morphology control of the electrode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells by using nanoparticles

Sentencas: Such unique morphology of the composite cathode led high electrochemical activity at 800degreesC.
Titulo: Morphology control of the electrode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells by using nanoparticles

Sentencas: It suggests that the intermediate temperature (less than 800degreesC) operation of SOFCs will be achieved by using composite particles.
Titulo: Morphology control of the electrode for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells by using nanoparticles
